features: 【Customize Watch Faces】There are multiple built-in dials for you to choose from, and you can upload your favorite pictures as your watch faces to suit your daily mood. In addition, each fitness watch equips with 1 stainless steel band and 1 silicone strap, which allows you to change according to different occasions. The integrated design of the transparent slightly curved glass and the aerospace-grade alloy watch body make it light and thin to wear.

【Answer/Dial Calls & Reminder】Women's wrist watches have built-in high-quality speakers that are perfect for bluetooth calling and receiving notification form Facebook, Twitter, Whatapp, Wechat, Instagram). You can get intelligent notifications for incoming calls, text messages, and social media alerts. With this wrist smartwatch, you won't have to worry about missing important calls or messages while your phones in the bag.

【Women's Health Tracking】Our fitness tracker watch with menstrual managerment, pregnancy tracking, sleep tracker, heart rate and blood pressure monitor which help you better grasp changes in your health. This health watches supports 122 sports modes like walking, running, cycling, yoga, etc, and automatically records daily steps, distance counter, calories burned, and active minutes. With this fitness watch for women and girls, you can have a healthier, more active life.

【Waterproof & Long Lasting Battery】The smartwatches adopts IP67 waterproof, which can easily cope with the waterproof test for daily life scenes such as hand washing and rain shower(It is not recommended to soak the smartwatch in water or place it in a water vapor environment). This sports activity watch is equipped with a 200 mAh large-capacity battery so that the step tracker can be used for 3-5 days when fully charged, and the standby time is about 20 days.

【Wide Compatibility】The digital watch womens contain Bluetooth 5.2 (supports Android 4.4+, IOS9.0+), compatible with most phones such as iPhone13/mini/pro/pro max/12/mini/pro/pro max/11/Pro/Max/Pro Max/XS/X/8/8 Plus/7/7 Plus/6/6s/6 Plus/6s Plus/5/se/5S/5C, HTC, Sony, LG, HUAWEI, OPPO, Vivo, etc.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Wonlex Stylish Women Smartwatch — Designed to Help you Keep a Positive Attitude and Have a Good Living Habit

SPECIFICATIONS DISPLAY: 1.2" Full Touch Screen, 240*240 Resolution COLOR: Silver, Gold WATERPROOF: IP 67 BLUETOOTH: BLE 5.2 SYSTEM: iOS 9.0 or above, Android 4.4 or above BATTERY LIFE: Working Time for 3-5 days, Standby Time for 20 Days CHARGE MODE: Magnetic USB Charge Cable PACKAGE CONTENT: 1 Women Watch, 2 Watch Bands, 1 Charging Cable, 1 User Manual

Main Interface Switching: Long press the main interface for 3 seconds to enter the selection dial interface, slide left and right to select the main interface, and click to confirm. Custom Dial: Enter the "DaFit" app and click - > dial selection - > Edit to select the dial you want.Find More Dials: Enter the "DaFit" app and click "dial selection" -> More dial settings. Information Push: This android smart watch supports Phone/Messages/WeChat/Facebook/Twitter/WhatsApp/Instagram/Skype/KakaoTalk/Line other application information push. This page only saves the last 5 information records, and you can turn on the corresponding switch according to your needs.Note that when the mobile phone opens the information reminder, it must set the notification right of the app to the mobile phone, otherwise the digital watch will not receive the reminder.

Menstrual Management Women's smart watch has a women's exclusive health monitoring mode, which can track your personal physiological cycle, pregnancy tracking and menstruation management. Remote Camera After connecting the mobile phone, the watch can be used as the remote control of the mobile phone camera. Open the "camera control" on the app side and click on the watch camera control page to trigger the snapshot of the mobile camera. Music Control After connecting the mobile phone, the ladies watch can control the pause/play of mobile phone music, the previous song, and the next song.

Sleep Monitoring The sucking function exercise is to carry out effective breathing and strengthen the respiratory muscles. Deep breathing can help you relieve stress. Weather Forecast The current weather and air quality information will be displayed on the weather interface. Slide up the weather interface to view the weather conditions for the next 6 days. The weather information can only be obtained after the app is connected. If the connection is disconnected for a long time, the weather information will not be updated. AI Voice You can operate your phone by voice, and it is more convenience when you are doing housework or shopping outside.

All-day-round Health Monitoring: 100+ sports modes are available: walking, running, cycling, basketball, football, badminton, rope skipping, and yoga. Health monitoring records heart rate, blood pressure, and blood oxygen related data. Heart Rate Measurement: click the screen in the heart rate interface to measure the current heart rate value. It can also be measured manually on the heart rate interface of the APP end (the data is only for reference and not for medical use)Blood Pressure: Click the screen in the blood pressure interface to measure the current blood pressure value. The icon flashes as in the test and slides right to exit. It can also be measured manually on the app side blood pressure interface(the data is only for reference and not for medical use)Blood Oxygen: Click the screen in the blood oxygen interface to measure the current blood oxygen value. The flashing icon indicates that the test is in progress, or it can be measured manually on the app end blood oxygen interface (the data is for reference only, not for medical use)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Bought this watch to replace my old one which broke. This watch is beautiful and the extra bands are a great plus. I get alot of compliments on this watch. Features are great. Only down side when connected to phone it cuts down on the volume of the phone and if it disconnects you can't hear any of your notifications or ringtones. Otherwise it was a great buy!!!

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Weather is inaccurate.
reviews.reviewText: Weather app inaccurate and steps can’t be right. Update. Finally got the weather working and outside of glitching occasionally, seems to be working well. Had to uninstall and re install app. Then had to close app and it finally allowed me to enter a zip code and seems to be working good. Steps still seem to be racking up awful fast, but hey. Very stylish watch.

reviews.reviewText: This watch works for some things but not all of it, while it is beautiful and well made there are issues with some of the apps, I got this for the blood pressure, sleep tracking and step tracking which all work so it's fine for me. But if you want more you may have some issues as I'm not sure the weather is very accurate all the time but I always used my phone for that.
